latestIgtvVideos.caption:
With the spirit of Diwali and the cheers of cricket coming together, festivities have doubled. @nestinsolutions celebrates both in their film! The film reinforces the brand's commitment to housing emotions, dreams, and aspirations, beyond mere structures. 

#Collab #worldcup #diwali

A superhero dadu, an adorable grandson and a heart-warming Diwali homecoming. @tynorofficial pitches itself as the support every hero needs to become a superhero!

#Collab #Tynor #Diwali2023

Diwali brings a lot of warmth, brightness and happiness to our lives. But this thoughtful campaign pauses and talks about being the light in someone else’s life.

Amidst our festive get-togethers, a lot of food goes to waste. The campaign shows how  the same food could brighten someone else’s Diwali. Simple, thoughtful and relatable!

cc: @shikharpanmasalaofficial 

#Collab #NekiKaRang

Times have changed, our priorities have changed, but why should we change those little things that make Diwali special? @epsonindia has created a heartfelt film that shows how a little effort can go a long way in celebrating Diwali the way it's intended.
 
A relatable film that strikes an emotional chord, and reminds us to make Diwali special this year.
 
#Collab #Diwali2023

On World EV Day, @blusmartindia is paying tribute to the real ‘drivers’ of change who work to transform the ride-hailing mobility landscape everyday… and make the world a cleaner, greener place!

#Collab #DriversOfChange #WorldEVDay

@himalaya_facecare is ‘washing away’ the beauty stereotypes with a hard-hitting campaign that encourages women to forget, move on, and embrace their natural glow! 

#Collab #WashAwayTheBS

@havells__india’s Rakshabandhan campaign called #RishtonKiGrooming is all kinds of warm. Despite all the pranks and quarrels, every brother takes the gift-giving tradition on Raksha Bandhan very seriously. The brand is helping them find the perfect gift this year with a range of personal grooming products for a unique, yet personal touch.

#Collab #RishtonKiGrooming

Is being modern… the same as being Western? With a powerful metaphor, @provilac_dairy is urging people to take off their ‘blindfolds’ and reconnect with the real Indian identity that is rich in culture, traditions, and Vedic knowledge. 

The brand is highlighting the declining demand for traditional Indian cow breeds, caused by a lack of awareness about their nutritional value. 

So, Provilac set out to revive the movement and deliver pure Desi Gir Cow A2 milk that is exceptionally rich in nutrients, especially in comparison to the milk that comes from crossbred European cows. 

#Collab #UNblind
